lso extend symptom relief into the following morning. This review outlines the pharmacological rationale and clinical evidence supporting IPX203 therapy, highlighting its potential to enhance motor control and improve patients' quality of life, thereby supporting a more personalised and sustained approach to PD management.", 'summary_1': ''}
