Fs, reinforcing their functional roles as susceptibility risk markers in AD. This work established an MR-TF-centered integrated regulatory network map of AD, revealing MR-TFs as factors that orchestrate gene deregulation in a region- and cell-context-dependent approach, and providing a robust foundation for mechanistic and translational investigations in neurodegeneration.", 'summary_1': ''}
